('98696','34055','5','Cosy House in small but neat residential complex with sea views'),
('98697','34056','5','The house is located in the popular residential area of Costa de la Calma in the southwest of Mallorca between Santa Ponsa and Paguera. The condominium was created in 1994 and has only a dozen houses and a community pool. The approx 150m² living space distributed over 2 residential floors and a garage in the basement. The ground floor has a living-dining room, a bathroom with shower and a kitchen with access to a cozy patio. On the 1st floor there are 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. From here you also have access to a ca 25m² roof terrace with a storage room for garden furniture. Features include among others the house air conditioning w / k for the bedrooms, gas central heating with radiators, a stylish fitted kitchen and PVC double glazed windows. From all levels and from the roof terrace you have a very beautiful panoramic sea views'),
